snippet.title: Aircraft In Pixels: Albatros D V
snippet.description:
This video is a gameplay trailer for version 0.1.7 of Aircraft in Pixels 2: Albatros D.V.

Aircraft in Pixels: Albatros D.V. is a video game wherein you construct a highly realistic WWI Albatros D.V fighter, decorate it with paint and decals, and optionally pose your finished creation against a variety of stunning backdrops to create desktop backgrounds and more.

Aircraft in Pixels is now in early release for Mac and PC at 
https://bomonroe.itch.io/aircraft-in-pixels-2 
with introductory pricing.

More info:
https://patreon.com/bomonroe
https://www.facebook.com/aircraftinpixels
